{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-28\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc","offset":1,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"---\ndescription: 编码前读什么 doc、变更后写哪\nglobs: docs/**,packages/**,apps/**\nalwaysApply: false\n---\n\n# 文档执行规范\n\n与 [docs-governance.mdc](./docs-governance.mdc)、[规则制定原则.mdc](./规则制定原则.mdc) 衔接。\n\n**冲突裁决**：当前代码/测试 > `codingRole.mdc` > 本规范 > `docs/AI/` > `docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/`（工程）≈ `docs/AI和人类/需求/`（产品）> `docs/人类/`。产品「做什么」与工程「怎么落」冲突时先对齐用户。\n\n## 编码前最小阅读集\n\n| 任务类型 | 必读 |\n|----------|------|\n| **任意非 trivial** | [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) → [需求/00](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/00-文档索引.md) |\n| Host / Session / 工作区 / 错误码 | [技术设计/19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) |\n| B/S / 选型 | [05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[18](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) |\n| 壳 / 导出 / 版本 | [07](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md)、[17](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/17-版本迁移与兼容策略.md) |\n| 用户 / 存档 | [10](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/10-用户与存档.md) |\n| CallCard / 运行时 | [01](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md) |\n| 动态出口 / Free | [15](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/15-动态出口与通话中工具事件.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) |\n| Studio UI | [03](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/03-编辑器界面需求.md)、[04](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md) |\n| 角色 / 人设 / 默认开场 | [11](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/11-角色与社交.md)、[50](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/50-对话与模型适配.md) |\n| 对话 / Composer / 场景组装 | [50](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/50-对话与模型适配.md)、[01](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md) |\n| 工具 Registry | [13](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/13-工具与能力注册.md) |\n| 内容校验 | [08](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md) |\n| 记忆 / MemoryCommit | [12](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/12-记忆模型.md) |\n\n## 变更后写哪\n\n| 变更 | 更新 |\n|------|------|\n| Host / Session / 工作区 / 错误码 | `技术设计文档/19` + `需求/00` / `06` |\n| 选型 / 拓扑 | `技术设计文档/05`、`18` |\n| 导出 / 版本拒载 | `技术设计文档/07`、`17` |\n| 产品行为 / UX / 验收 | `需求/` 对应编号 |\n| 代码落地模块地图 | 用户明示后写 `docs/AI/` |\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":40,"fileSize":2751,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":40},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-28\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_5","startedAtMs":"1784721445793","completedAtMs":"1784721446082"},"model_call_id":"6f083b9c-715b-401c-bee6-8dedacfc25fa-6-fg9n","session_id":"9981a650-ae57-4a10-b6bb-90832abae14e","timestamp_ms":1784721446115}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-26\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/charactersApi.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 角色库 BFF 请求：读写 data/characters（经 /api/characters）。\n\t* 仅返回 CharacterDef 形状；投影到 CharacterSummary 在 bis。\n\t*/\nimport type { CharacterDef } from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\nimport { parseStudioApiJson } from \"@studio-v2/src/utils/ajaxHelper/studioApiClient\";\n\nexport type CharactersListData = {\n\tcharacters: CharacterDef[];\n};\n\nexport type CharacterOneData = {\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef;\n};\n\n/** GET /api/characters：列出磁盘角色 */\nexport async function fetchCharacterDefs(): Promise<CharacterDef[]> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/characters\");\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharactersListData>(res);\n\treturn data.characters;\n}\n\n/** GET /api/characters/:agentId */\nexport async function fetchCharacterDef(\n\tagentId: string,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`);\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** PUT /api/characters/:agentId：整卡落盘 */\nexport async function putCharacterDef(\n\tagentId: string,\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"PUT\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ character }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** POST /api/characters：新建落盘 */\nexport async function postCharacterDef(\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/characters\", {\n\t\tmethod: \"POST\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ character }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** DELETE /api/characters/:agentId */\nexport async function deleteCharacterDef(agentId: string): Promise<void> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"DELETE\",\n\t});\n\tawait parseStudioApiJson<{ ok: true }>(res);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":66,"fileSize":2064,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/charactersApi.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":66},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-26\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_3","startedAtMs":"1784721445787","completedAtMs":"1784721446083"},"model_call_id":"6f083b9c-715b-401c-bee6-8dedacfc25fa-6-fg9n","session_id":"9981a650-ae57-4a10-b6bb-90832abae14e","timestamp_ms":1784721446120}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-27\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md","limit":60},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 角色库与人设编辑（代码事实）\n\n> 对照：`apps/studioV2` 角色页 + 故事编辑器角色 FormModal。  \n> 产品字段意图见 [需求 11](../../AI和人类/需求/11-角色与社交.md)。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8：角色/编辑器锚点均磁盘 + API；`MOCK_EDITOR_CHARACTERS` 已删）。\n\n## 1. 磁盘五人真源（已接通）\n\n真源：`data/characters/*.json` ↔ Next `/api/characters`（ajaxProxy：`library/api/charactersApi.ts`）。  \n**已删除：** `MOCK_CHARACTERS` / `mockCharactersData.ts` / `listMockCharacters` / `commitUpdateCharacterMock` 等角色业务 mock 入口（无兼容壳）。\n\n| agentId | 显示名 | personalityCode | 备注 |\n|---------|--------|-----------------|------|\n| `lanxing` | 澜星姐姐 | ENFJ | 电话 2267070 |\n| `xiaopi` | 小皮 | ENFP | |\n| `qiang-shushu` | 强叔叔 | ESTP | |\n| `zhang-boss` | 张老板 | INTJ | |\n| `bai-bansian` | 白半仙 | INFJ | 号码 010 |\n\n- **来源意图：** doubaoSister 正式角色设定稿「错误电话之前」必要 5 人。  \n- **落盘：** 正式五人 JSON 在 `data/characters/`；库页列表经 `fetchCharacterDefs()` → **走** `/api/characters`。  \n- **增删改：** `commitCreateCharacter` / `commitDeleteCharacter` / `commitSaveCharacterDetail` 写盘后刷新可见。\n\n## 2. 投影与表单贯通\n\n```text\nCharacterSummary (typeFiles/.../characterSummary.ts)\n  ↔ toCharacterDetailFormValues / applyCharacterDetailForm\n  ↔ CharacterDetailFormValues (Formik)\n  ↔ characterDefToSummary / mergeDetailFormIntoCharacterDef  (落盘 CharacterDef)\n```\n\n关键文件：\n\n- Items：`bis/.../characterDetailFormItems.ts`  \n  - 基本信息：`CHARACTER_BASIC_ITEMS`（含音色 Select）  \n  - 提示词：`CHARACTER_PROMPT_ITEMS`（含 **人格类型** `persona.personalityCode`）  \n- 校验：展示字段编辑态**全必填**（含 personalityCode）。  \n- MBTI 选项：`typeFiles/library/characters/persona/personalityCodeOptions.ts`（16 型）。  \n- 音色选项：`typeFiles/library/characters/realtime/realtimeVoiceOptions.ts`（引擎只存 `voiceId` 字符串）。\n\n## 3. 哪里能编角色\n\n| 入口 | 行为 |\n|------|------|\n| 角色库详情页 | `CharacterDetailEditForm` + BASIC/PROMPT items；保存走 API |\n| 故事编辑器选中锚点 | `StoryEditorCharacterModals` 复用同一套 items；打开前 `fetchCharacterDef` |\n| 画布「添加角色」 | 先走精简 `CREATE_CHARACTER_*` → `commitCreateCharacter`，再可编辑详情槽 |\n\n画布角色锚点 **打开时**由 `bundle.participants` + `/api/characters` 的 displayName 生成（`diskBundleGraph`）；`pendingCardCount` 由当前包内卡归属统计。**不是**独立 mock 数组；完整人设仍按 agentId 从 API 取。\n\n## 4. persona.personalityCode 业务理解\n\n- Studio：Select 写入投影字段；保存时 trim 后进 CharacterDef。  \n- 引擎：见 [05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md](./05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md)。  \n- UI helperText 已写明会进 Composer systemHard（演示口径；Host 真跑另议）。\n\n## 5. 已知小不一致（勿当 bug 乱修扩大范围）\n\n- 部分磁盘 `voiceId`（如 `zh_child_boy`、`zh_male_elder`）**不在** `REALTIME_VOICE_OPTIONS` 枚举内；下拉可能显示空/异常，属音色枚举未扩全，与 MBTI 任务无关。  ","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":62,"fileSize":3445,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":60},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-89724e27-0482-4115-b998-97acc30f4719-27\nfc_02644a5a-d12d-9323-97c4-15496f77e069_4","startedAtMs":"1784721445790","completedAtMs":"1784721446096"},"model_call_id":"6f083b9c-715b-401c-bee6-8dedacfc25fa-6-fg9n","session_id":"9981a650-ae57-4a10-b6bb-90832abae14e","timestamp_ms":1784721446135}
